Dia. 04 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 is the \cf1\b vital point for the capturing race\cf0\b0 . Whenever White got to play here, Black was in trouble. The opponent's vital point is my vital.
\par
\par After White 2, Black fills the liberty at 3 and wins the capturing race.
\par
\par Therefore\b  Black didn't have to answer White's pae threat\b0 .
\par
\par }
